<div class="row">
    
    <h1 class="heading-1">Hi!</h1>
    <p>My name is Claire Sosset, I'm a front-end developer based in Paris.</p>
    
    <p>After studies in the field of new technologies, and a year of training in alternation within a communication agency, I am currently working at <a rel="external" href="http://octaveoctave.com">Octave &amp; Octave</a> as lead front-end developer.</p>

    <p>I use mainly HTML5, CSS3 and JavaScript. Curious nature, I like trying new tools on my spare time as Backbone, Require, Ruby on Rails and Nodejs.</p>
    
    <h1 class="heading-2">Some works</h1>

    <ul class="list">
        <% @projects.each do |project| %>

            <li class="list__item">
                <div class="list__picture">
                    <% if project.cover.file? %>
                        <%= link_to image_tag(project.cover.url(:medium), :alt => "", :class => "picture"), project.url, :rel => "external" %>
                    <% end %>
                </div>
                
                <div class="list__txt">
                    <%= link_to project.title, project.url, :rel => "external" %>
                    <small><%= raw project.infos %></small>
                    <span class="list__tags"><%= project.tags %></span>    
                </div>
            </li>
            
        <% end %>
    </ul>
</div>


